        "body": "<p>The link you posted contains the instructions to use the library via Gradle, eg (in your ´build.gradle´):<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>repositories {\n  mavenCentral()\n}\n\ndependencies {\n  compile 'com.google.apis:google-api-services-blogger:v3-rev55-1.23.0'\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
